title: DAO
body:
Ideas
--

Should we DAO this? 

By owning Nero One (N1) token, you can vote and create proposals. 

Proposals mostly would be related to my NFT Collections. However, if there's any cool idea please submit a new proposal and we can get everyone to vote :)

Example Proposal : 
`Owning 10 tokens can get you free N1 Card NFT`

So it's up to the DAO and I will do my best to apply it :)

Vote
--

Do you agree to go for this DAO ? **Yeahhh** or **No**
